🧭 Commonshub Onboarding — System Flow

CREATOR (browser)
        │
        ▼
FRONTEND (Flow UI)
        │
        │  step input / option selection
        ▼
ONBOARDING API (orchestrator)
        │
        ├──────────────► SESSION STORE
        │                 (ephemeral state)
        │
        ├──────────────► LLM STEP ENGINE
        │                 (returns options + recommendation)
        │
        ▼
STEP RESPONSE → FRONTEND

User iterates until:

PHASE A COMPLETE (commit)
        │
        ▼
ATOMIC PERSIST


# 🔁 Resume / Magic Link Path (no re-onboarding)

CREATOR clicks resume link
        │
        ▼
FRONTEND (Resume Route /resume?token=…)
        │
        ▼
BACKEND: RESUME TOKEN RESOLVER
        │
        ├── validates token (not expired / not revoked)
        ├── loads session state + blueprint_id
        ├── rotates token (issue new token, invalidate old)
        ▼
NEXT-STATE ROUTER (backend)
        │
        ├── if phase_completed != "A" → invalid → start New
        ├── if phase_completed == "A" and purchase_success != true
        │        → route to Plan Select (UI)
        ├── if purchase_success == true and provisioning_complete != true
        │        → route to Provisioning Status (UI)
        └── if provisioning_complete == true
                 → route to Dashboard (UI)



💾 Artifact Creation Layer


At commit:

ONBOARDING API
   │
   ├──► BLUEPRINT STORE (authoritative)
   │
   ├──► DIAGNOSTIC TRANSCRIPT STORE (append-only)
   │
   └──► OUTCOME / STATS STORE (computed)

   Then:

   	resume_token generated
	provisioning invite email triggered


