Provisioning trigger

GET  /v1/resume/{token}          → returns next_route + blueprint_id/session_id
POST /v1/resume/{token}/rotate   → rotates token after successful use

Resume token must resolve to blueprint_id + phase state; Blueprint is the authoritative resumable artifact.

POST /v1/provision/{blueprint_id}

